name: Individual Rainbow Primitives
description:
Individual Rainbow Primitives with a seed based on the owners tezos-addresses, noise-fields render differently for every owner.

Click/Tap to reset noise-field lines.
Arrow-Down to toggle clearing-mode.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.collide, p5.createloop and post5.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
